Mjolnir.jl
============

A source-level MATLAB -> idiomatic-Julia converter.

Third-party components
----------------------

At build time (deps/build.jl), Mjolnir fetches and compiles the community
MIT-licensed MATLAB grammar for tree-sitter:

  tree-sitter-matlab
  Copyright (c) 2023 Alan Cristoffer
  https://github.com/acristoffers/tree-sitter-matlab
  License: MIT
  Pinned revision: c2390a59016f74e7d5f75ef09510768b4f30217e

Mjolnir links the system tree-sitter runtime (libtree-sitter) via FFI; that
library is provided by the host system and is not redistributed here.

Octave, when present, is used only as an out-of-process differential-testing
oracle (a separate subprocess). Its source is never read and it is never linked;
Mjolnir contains no Octave (GPL) code.

